Very basic requirements of what program should be able to do

From modem side:
  Obtain network signal
  
Program side:
  Function to check and switch to another sim should credit balance be depleated on call
  Ability to send and receive SMS and or MMS messages
  Ability to make and receive phone calls
    Normal landline numbers
    Normal cellular numbers
    International calling
    USSD calling
  Simultaneously interact with each port should a call be incoming on any number allocated to the modem.
